and this and this.

72
00:03:01,332 --> 00:03:04,834
Now, if you'll excuse me...
Where are you going?

73
00:03:04,836 --> 00:03:06,602
Oh, I'm going to go get a drink

74
00:03:06,604 --> 00:03:08,671
while this is still a party.

75
