A frapin cuvee?
Easy, Prince Charles.

78
00:03:22,687 --> 00:03:24,954
Where I'm from,
you wait your turn in line.

79
00:03:24,956 --> 00:03:26,055
Oh, I'm so sorry,

80
00:03:26,057 --> 00:03:27,590
but I thought
you'd been served.

81
00:03:27,592 --> 00:03:30,159
