and order your Miller Lite.

84
00:03:36,567 --> 00:03:38,134
Macallan 25, neat.

85
00:03:38,136 --> 00:03:40,236
Why don't you put a banana
in it for my man here?

86
00:03:40,238 --> 00:03:42,238
