223
00:09:08,621 --> 00:09:10,187
With sympathy?

224
00:09:10,189 --> 00:09:13,324
- With pity.
- I wasn't. Rachel...

225
00:09:13,326 --> 00:09:15,092
Listen to me.
There are other schools.

226
00:09:15,094 --> 00:09:17,728
Don't.

227
00:09:17,730 --> 00:09:20,331
Yeah. I won't.

228
00:09:22,334 --> 00:09:25,369
