243
00:10:04,477 --> 00:10:05,676
Then what?

244
00:10:05,678 --> 00:10:08,913
It's just not right.

245
00:10:11,183 --> 00:10:14,819
Yeah.

246
00:10:18,490 --> 00:10:21,091
It was a pleasure meeting you.

247
00:10:21,093 --> 00:10:23,260
- [Mouthing words]
- [Chuckles]

248
00:10:25,897 --> 00:10:27,731
