251
00:10:30,236 --> 00:10:31,735
I was caressing her lovely hand

252
00:10:31,737 --> 00:10:33,170
with my lovely lips.

253
00:10:33,172 --> 00:10:34,505
You know what I mean.

254
00:10:34,507 --> 00:10:36,607
